Package com.saurabh.service

Provides necessary Service Layers for each Entity which mediates the communication between the REST Controller and the Repository.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CourseService
    This Interface is used to declare methods for CRUD operations of Course Entity through Course Service Layer
    FeeService
    This Interface is used to declare methods for CRUD operations of Fee Entity through Fee Service Layer
    StudentService
    This Interface is used to declare methods for CRUD operations of Student Entity through Student Service Layer
    TeacherService
    This Interface is used to declare methods for CRUD operations of Teacher Entity through Teacher Service Layer
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CourseServiceImpl
    This Class is a Service Layer between the Course Repository and Course REST Controller.
    FeeServiceImpl
    This Class is a Service Layer between the Fee Repository and Fee REST Controller.
    StudentServiceImpl
    This Class is a Service Layer between the Student Repository and Student REST Controller.
    TeacherServiceImpl
    This Class is a Service Layer between the Teacher Repository and Teacher REST Controller.
